<holidayType guid="e06b2794-470c-4251-b475-ee5f7e9057f8" id="24049" nodeName="Chalets" isDoc="" updated="2021-12-29T10:26:57.9930000Z" parentGUID="9e164d02-7242-4fd2-a479-d5af2cd75823" nodeTypeAlias="holidayType" templateAlias="HolidayType" sortOrder="4" published="false" isBlueprint="false">
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">
<div>
<p><img src="/media/13067434/first-example-of-inghams-chalet-food.jpg" alt="Chalet Holidays" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>Chalets provide a smaller alternative to our Chalet Hotels, with a personal ‘home from home’ atmosphere, where you will be well looked after by your friendly chalet hosts.</strong></p>
<br />
<p><strong>Half-Board PLUS Chalet Meals</strong></p>
<p>Our chalet cuisine shown on our <a data-udi="umb://document/571381e477bb4408800e0126e9f89cfc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/571381e477bb4408800e0126e9f89cfc}" title="Chalet Hotels">Chalet Hotels</a> page, with a daily buffet breakfast, packed lunch and afternoon tea 5 days per week, and dinner 6 days per week, including one barbecue or al fresco evening. With their smaller kitchens and staff teams however, chalets do not include a hot option at breakfast, and dinner is a fixed table d’hôte menu of four courses, comprising canapés &amp; apéritif, starter, main course and dessert, followed by tea/coffee &amp; chocolates.<br /><br /></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>What’s included</h2>
<ul>
<li>Friendly service from your Inghams chalet hosts</li>
<li>Comfortable accommodation with private en suite bedrooms</li>
</ul>
<p><strong> Half-Board PLUS:</strong><br />includes the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>Daily buffet breakfast</li>
<li>Packed lunches</li>
<li>Afternoon tea/coffee &amp; cake</li>
<li>Excellent 4 or 5 course evening meals with an apéritif, choice of complimentary quality wines, tea / coffee &amp; chocolates</li>
<li>Weekly barbecue or al fresco evening</li>
<li>Knowledgable staff to help you get the most out of your holiday</li>
<li>FREE Wi-Fi in public areas</li>
<li>All non-smoking properties</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Complimentary Chalet Wines</h2>
<p>Our choice of wines is selected in conjunction with our good friends, Nicolas and Véronique Perret, and their long established Savoie wine business. Nicolas is a qualified ‘Master of Wine’, and has helped us select two contrasting whites, two choice reds and a rosé for you to enjoy, unlimited, throughout dinner each evening.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Our Chalet Hosts</h2>
<p>Our chalet hosts are chosen for their friendly and helpful attitude, whilst our chefs and their teams are professionally trained to provide consistently enjoyable restaurant-standard cuisine. At all times your Resort Representative is also on hand to help out with their local knowledge, and to arrange local restaurant bookings on the staff’s one evening off duty per week.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Our Chalets</h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/36fdc86201b04b4fb9296fb29c7f1981" href="/{localLink:umb://document/36fdc86201b04b4fb9296fb29c7f1981}" title="Chalet Tirol"><strong>Chalet Tirol</strong></a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen"><strong>Mayrhofen</strong></a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria"><strong>Austria</strong></a>, has an informal and welcoming atmosphere.</p>
<p><strong>New for Summer 2018</strong>, <a data-udi="umb://document/1196adbd15484919b16e05301559d3c7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1196adbd15484919b16e05301559d3c7}" title="Chalet Linda"><strong>Chalet Linda</strong></a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739}" title="Kitzbuhel"><strong>Kitzbühel</strong></a>, <strong>Austria</strong>, has a rustic feel in this sophisticated and chic resort.</p>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>General Information - Chalets</strong></p>
<p>Vegetarian options are always available on our menus at no extra cost, and other special diets can be catered for at a cost of £35 per person per week, if booked in advance. All Chalets are entirely non-smoking. Property ratings displayed on the accommodation page(s) are our own, and are not to be confused with any 'official' star rating systems. Further information can be found in our <a href="/{localLink:66d6dfd2-b127-48e8-b6d8-228d6e59ea65}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">Terms and Conditions</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
